info.name: 06. Use Case - Antenatal Care (ANC)
info.description:
For **complete repository for all SATUSEHAT use-cases** please access our public workspaces : [Postman Workspaces](https://s.id/PostmanSATUSEHAT) For **detailed SATUSEHAT use-cases import link** please see : [Postman Public Kemkes Link](https://link.kemkes.go.id/PostmanSATUSEHAT) Any information about SATUSEHAT FHIR Profile could be accessed through [Simplifier FHIR Profile](https://simplifier.net/guide/SATUSEHAT-FHIR-R4-Implementation-Guide/Home/FHIRProfiles?version=current) For this Folder 06. ANC, there are several parameterized variables, please kindly check folder-variables as well as tests on POST (Encounter, ServiceRequest, Specimen) As well as GET (EpisodeOfCare) Please make sure that you have inserted Org_id in your environment before testing | **Folder History** | **Editor** | Date | | --- | --- | --- | | Major Update according to latest Playbook, introduced parameterization | [thomas.chaidir@dto.kemkes.go.id

](https://mailto:thomas.chaidir@dto.kemkes.go.id)[luthfi.qonitah@dto.kemkes.go.id](https://mailto:luthfi.qonitah@dto.kemkes.go.id) | 01-02-2024 |
